      <p id="Par21">The minimum founder set problem and the minimum segmentation problem are connected: any segmentation <italic>S</italic> with segments of length at least <italic>L</italic> induces in an obvious way a founder set of size <inline-formula id="IEq68"><alternatives><tex-math id="M137">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
