      <p id="Par22">Our main result is an algorithm that solves the minimum segmentation problem in <italic>O</italic>(<italic>mn</italic>) time (linear in the input size). The solution normally does not uniquely define a founder set of <inline-formula id="IEq78"><alternatives><tex-math id="M157">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
