      <p id="Par30">To reconstruct a segmentation corresponding to the found solution <italic>M</italic>(<italic>n</italic>), we build along with the values <italic>M</italic>(<italic>k</italic>) an array of size <italic>n</italic> whose <italic>k</italic>th element, for each <inline-formula id="IEq123"><alternatives><tex-math id="M251">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
