        <sec id="FPar2">
          <title>
            <italic>Example 1</italic>
          </title>
          <p id="Par34">Consider the following example, where <inline-formula id="IEq154"><alternatives><tex-math id="M299">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
