				\begin{document}$$d_{k-1}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M494"><mml:msub><mml:mi>d</mml:mi><mml:mrow><mml:mi>k</mml:mi><mml:mo>-</mml:mo><mml:mn>1</mml:mn></mml:mrow></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="13015_2019_147_Article_IEq248.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> accordingly. This idea is implemented in Algorithm 2. Notice the new line <inline-formula id="IEq249"><alternatives><tex-math id="M495">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
