          <p>For position <italic>j</italic>, denote by <italic>p</italic>(<italic>j</italic>) the number of non-scaling touches of <italic>j</italic>. We are to prove that <inline-formula id="IEq286"><alternatives><tex-math id="M571">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
