      <sec id="Sec6">
        <title>Modification of the pBWT</title>
        <p id="Par47">We are to modify the basic pBWT construction algorithm in order to compute the sequence <inline-formula id="IEq328"><alternatives><tex-math id="M655">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
