          <p>For convenience, let us recall Eq. (<xref rid="Equ3" ref-type="">3</xref>) defined in the beginning of this section:<disp-formula id="Equ4"><label>3 revisited</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M829">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
