            <bold>Lemma 5</bold>
          </title>
          <p id="Par58"><italic>Consider a set of recombinants</italic><inline-formula id="IEq448"><alternatives><tex-math id="M899">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
